{"tid":2305242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"運輸處女工程師確診，西九龍政府合署辦公地點需清潔消毒","createTime":"2020-11-29T13:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T09:08:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3115676522c3790d6d03ca7c3ffa6b1a5607b3eb","tid":2305242,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dIcZ6B.1Dw8EmS4w.yWdUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni43NjkyMzA3NjkyMzA3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/dwKTVqodIfFUFiEoqTbImA--~B/aD01NTg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/b5220b5a7f9040279a4b7a116b6901a4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdIcZ6B.1Dw8EmS4w.yWdUw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni43NjkyMzA3NjkyMzA3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdwKTVqodIfFUFiEoqTbImA--~B%2FaD01NTg7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb5220b5a7f9040279a4b7a116b6901a4&h=84a1dea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港肺炎疫情爆發第4波，運輸署表示，今日(29日)得悉一名女工程師確診，其辦公室地點位於九龍油麻地海庭道11號西九龍政府合署南座16樓，她最近一次上班日期為上周四(24日)。而該樓層並非公眾樓層，並不對外開放，有關工作地點亦會按照中心指引安排全面清潔和消毒，包括所有公用設施。<br />\n<br />\n該名人員最近沒有外遊紀錄，於辦公室工作時均佩戴口罩及遵守其他防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/運輸署女工程師確診-西九龍政府合署辦公地點需清潔消毒-111136704.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%90%88%E7%BD%B2%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E9%9C%80%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92-111136704.html&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=f5634e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/運輸署女工程師確診-西九龍政府合署辦公地點需清潔消毒-111136704.html</a>"},{"pid":"858a12f65afabbb5b03ed442d7f181cdfb20215c","tid":2305242,"uid":41087,"like":144,"dislike":6,"score":138,"cited